{"word":"προσδέρκομαι","slug":"προσδέρκομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>προσδέρκομαι</b></el> <el>(doric <el>ποτι-δέρκομαι</el>) (<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-δέρξομαι</el>) (aor2 <a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>act.</a></a> <el>-έδρᾰκον</el>) (aor1 <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a> <el>-εδέρχθην</el>) (<a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <el>-δέδορκα</el>) </el><p/><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to look at, behold</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to look closely</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}